snippet.title: Advance Wars 1+2: Re-Boot Camp - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
New intel arrives on Advance Wars 1+2 Re-Boot Camp! Learn more about additions to the two full campaigns including voiced Commanding Officers, additional modes, & more!

Advance Wars 1+2: Re-Boot Camp arrives on Nintendo Switch April 8! https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/advance-wars-1-plus-2-re-boot-camp-switch/
